tags.note:name: The actual name of the region is just "Montréal". I have modified the name here to reduce confusion when displaying search results, since almost all users will want the city, not the region.
tags.note:wikipedia:en: There is no English Wikipedia page corresponding to the administrative region's Wikidata item. The English page "Urban agglomeration of Montreal" covers both the territory equivalent (admin_level=6) and administrative region (admin_level=5).
